item.title: About
item.description: I’m Edwin Kofler, an aspiring web developer. My most current project is an interactive periodic table. The most recent public version is here, which is a few months outdated. (I can’t deploy the more recent versions because they have a back-end). I hope to deploy the complete site before November. Check out my GitHub here.
